title: Analysis of Cars
text:
Letâ€™s investigate the relationship between fuel efficiency (mpg) and engine displacement (disp) from the mtcars dataset. Those variables have a correlation of -0.85.

library(tidyverse)
data(mtcars)
mtcars |>
  ggplot(aes(mpg, disp)) + 
  geom_point(color="dodgerblue4", size=2)
